flowchart LR
  C[Client] --> E[AuthAPI Express]
  E --> MW[Security + Validation + Logging]
  MW --> R[Auth Routes]
  R --> B[bcrypt]
  R --> J[JWT Sign/Verify]
  R --> P[Prisma]
  P --> D[(Postgres)]

sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant E as Express
  participant P as Prisma
  participant D as Postgres
  C->>E: POST /auth/refresh
  E->>E: verify refresh JWT
  E->>P: find refresh token
  P->>D: SELECT token row
  D-->>P: token row
  E->>P: revoke old + insert new token
  P->>D: UPDATE + INSERT
  E-->>C: new access + refresh tokens
